Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天迟到不太好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发消息给她看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大家在等你啊～～）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  回消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…鲑鱼好疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是让我们先去的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打个电话给她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  我们先去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早起来弹了下吉太就变成这样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（恭喜大家毕业！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没到齐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同学  琴吹同学  田井中同学  平泽同学还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了送给毕业生的花后就去大礼堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到毕业典礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要和学姐们说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太好重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是轻音部  总是挣扎在死亡线上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  撞到了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  平泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  破了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上来的时候摔了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧把替换的紧身裤放在我这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  超能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是手忙脚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你们还没写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写给山中老师的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下小律你们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在毕业典礼的日子发生这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  有刘海遮着看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  毕业典礼能顺利结束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  没事的  已经没什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就请在校生为毕业生戴上花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让她们给你们戴花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  写一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给小佐和的惊喜礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全班同学的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带来了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  无意中就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同学  你们快到里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个在典礼中要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当扇子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在毕业典礼中不需要那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给小佐和保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这样拿着怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在典礼中一直都这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  好像大礼堂和平时感觉不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毕业典礼…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就开始第85届樱丘女子高级中学的毕业典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请校长致词  起立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…各位毕业生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有各位家长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业生的各位在这三年间有很多的相识  也发生了很多故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定产生了很多美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太在意了  无法集中精神听校长讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们教职全员都从心底祝福大家今后表现活跃以及身体健康
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很在意唯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  起立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  刚才隐藏了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食？  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是小猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授予毕业证书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班代表请上台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意着唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常在意的样子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业生起立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我传话给唯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说佐和子老师很在意你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉唯是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪的传话  佐和子老师失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和失败？  什么失败？  为什么传这话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪想向我传达什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业生答词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到和和发言了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答词
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢大家今天为我们的毕业典礼而相聚到场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回首往事  在这所学校度过的三年非常充实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才典礼时太让人在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也非常在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  小佐和失败是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我说的是佐和子老师在担心你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我这里的时候还是担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  别管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你出的乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯写好了吗  纸笺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要抓紧时间写咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你笔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小佐和  祝你幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不太对吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚的话倒还可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都写上去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这话很打击吧  很打击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那修正一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先回一趟教室啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要发毕业证书给你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业典礼的时候你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意得都不能集中精神参加典礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在保一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下你就懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就告诉我  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回教室吧  佐和子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}毕业证书\N平沢唯\N十一月二十七日  生\N右方人士已经修完本校的高级中学课程\N特此证书\N樱丘女子高级中学\N校长  冲山阳二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯也毕业了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的毕业证书都没发错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认过后妥善保管带回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜欢这个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的高中生活到此也就告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是我首个担任班主任的班级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常欣慰看到大家精神饱满地迎来这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也多保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…解散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有份谢礼要送给老师您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在谁手里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小唯  就拜托你赠送了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是返还优胜旗用的曲子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（运动会开幕式用的音乐，多用于甲子园）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山中老师  谢谢您的栽培
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说典礼上你拿的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次做班主任遇到你们实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空要记得回来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘等着你们呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哟  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:30.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  好酷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
