Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…纯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去爵士研活动室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己多注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓也要去音乐室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人要为姐姐庆贺毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆贺…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆贺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不能和姐姐穿同样的制服有点遗憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过姐姐每次都走在我前面一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐嘛  也是没办法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我也会好好祝贺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能和轻音部一起…拍一张照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  正中间正中间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要上同一所大学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请继续搞音乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的时候…真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是帅气或者好听之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业旅行去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和真受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会不知道还来不来活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来蹭茶喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去下学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见  和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后电话联系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（祝贺你们毕业）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（最喜欢山中老师  圭子）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫人怎么擦嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想今天我来倒茶的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们一直也没怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力拉新人进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对  绝对  绝对不会废部的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我之前一直没有好好向学姐们道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我写了感谢信…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是刚刚才写好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  现在能读吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊  好的  请随意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都写了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐们才是  恭喜你们毕业…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要毕业…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不整理活动室或者整天喝茶我也不责怪你们了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要毕业…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额头怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明明是毕业典礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明该祝贺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有带着创可贴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来打算不哭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要笑着送别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会好好继承轻音部…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…小猪也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们一年级时候的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比现在的梓喵还要年轻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个也送给你  五枚花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们很像呢  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装什么酷嘛  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就唯一个人太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  有首歌希望你能听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  连澪也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为梓喵创作的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  这是我的台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========================
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:39.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天使にふれたよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:47.85,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　思い出のカケラに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:54.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名前をつけて保存するなら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宝物」がピッタリだね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:08.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　心の容量が　いっぱいになるくらいに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:14.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過ごしたね　トキメキ色の毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:19.52,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なじんだ　制服と上ばき
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.77,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ホワイトボードの落書き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.84,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日の入り口に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:32.15,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おいてかなくちゃ　いけないのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:40.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもね会えたよ　すてきな天使に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:44.06,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卒業は終わりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:48.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これからも　仲間だから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:56.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒の写真達　おそろのキーホルダー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつまでも輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:06.68,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと　その笑顔　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駅のホーム　河原の道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:19.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離れてても　同じ空見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:25.68,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ユニゾンで歌おー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:37.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもね　会えたよ　素敵な天使に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:41.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卒業は終わりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:45.84,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これからも　仲間だから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:53.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好きって言うなら　大大好きって返すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.83,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れ物　もうないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:04.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと永遠に　一緒だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:39.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「相遇天使」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:47.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回忆的碎片　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:54.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取个名字来保存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就应该是「宝物」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:08.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错　无比充实地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:14.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度过缤纷的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:19.52,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟悉的校服和拖鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有白板上的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天的入口处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:32.15,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须全部留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:40.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　相遇了　美丽的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:44.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业不会是终点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:48.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:56.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同拥有的照片　一起持有的挂坠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都那么闪烁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:06.68,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这永远的笑容　道声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站的站台　河岸的走道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:19.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使相隔遥远　遥望同一天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:25.68,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同声齐唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:37.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　相遇了　美丽的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:41.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业不会是终点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:45.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:53.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那声「最喜欢」　换回「最最喜欢」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有遗憾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:04.24,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们永远会在一起
